@base = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### Register buyer baru
POST {{base}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Buyer",
  "email": "testbuyer@mail.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login (pakai akun demo buyer)
# @name loginBuyer
POST {{base}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "buyer@seapedia.com",
  "password": "buyer12345"
}

### Login sebagai admin (langsung aktif, tanpa select-role)
POST {{base}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@seapedia.com",
  "password": "admin12345"
}

### Contoh select-role kalau punya >1 role (pakai temp token dari login)
@tempToken = PASTE_TEMP_TOKEN_DI_SINI
POST {{base}}/select-role
Authorization: Bearer {{tempToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "role": "seller" }

### Profile (pakai token dari login di atas)
@token = PASTE_TOKEN_DI_SINI
GET {{base}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Tambah role baru untuk akun sendiri (misal buyer ingin jadi seller juga)
POST {{base}}/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "role": "seller" }
